# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ViLoLabs — HTTP headers (Cloudflare Pages reads this file like _redirects)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# CACHE POLICY — the important part:
#   Our HTML, JS, CSS and JSON must ALWAYS revalidate, so the moment we push an
#   update EVERY returning visitor gets it. Without this, code files were cached
#   for 4h (max-age=14400) → after a fix, returning browsers kept running the old,
#   broken build until their cache expired. Revalidation is cheap: the browser
#   sends an ETag check → 304 (use cache) if unchanged, fresh bytes if we shipped
#   a change. Heavy, rarely-changing media (clipart, emoji, og cards) is cached.
#
# Rules apply top-to-bottom; for a shared header the LAST matching rule wins —
# so the media overrides below take precedence over the catch-all default.

/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=()

# Cloudflare Pages defaults .js/.css to max-age=14400. Try to force the shared
# app code to always-revalidate via exact paths so code updates ship instantly.
/assets/share.js
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate
/assets/share.css
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate
/assets/db.js
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate
/worksheets/worksheet-seo.js
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate
/tools/tool-seo.js
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate
/tools/shared.css
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate
/blog/shared/blog.css
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate

# ── Rarely-changing media → cache for a day (safe to be slightly stale) ──
/assets/library/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=86400
/assets/emoji/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=86400
/assets/og/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=86400
/assets/pages/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=86400
/assets/favicon.svg
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=86400
/assets/logo.svg
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=86400
